| IGN = 8.2/10<ref>{{cite web | author=Mark Bozon | date=September 8, 2006 | title=IGN: Mega Man ZX Review | url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2006/09/08/mega-man-zx-review | work=IGN | access-date=2009-08-18 | archive-date=2012-06-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614062200/http://ds.ign.com/articles/731/731859p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>
| NP = 8.5/10<ref>{{cite magazine |magazine=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] | publisher=[[Nintendo|Nintendo of America]] |date=October 2006 | issue=208 | page=90 | title=Now Playing}}</ref>
| Play = 9/10<ref>{{cite magazine |date=September 2006|title=Reviews: Mega Man ZX|magazine=Play Magazine | publisher=Fusion Publishing |page=65}}</ref>
| XPlay = {{Rating|3|5}}<ref>{{cite web | author=D. F. Smith | date=October 30, 2006 | title=Mega Man ZX for Nintendo DS - Reviews - G4tv.com | url=https://g4tv.com/games/ds/35460/mega-man-zx/review | work=G4tv | access-date=2009-08-18 | archive-date=2017-10-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012044102/http://g4tv.com/games/ds/35460/mega-man-zx/review/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>
}}
该游戏整体获得了多数好评，在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得到了76的总分（满分100）。<ref name="mc"/>和洛克人Zero系列类似，该游戏也被比作是“[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]上的经典洛克人系列”。该游戏的高难度模式被一些评论家给予好评，也被另一些评论家给予批评。游戏的玩法以及关卡的设计获得了好评，但评论家们认为游戏令人迷惑的地图设计以及令人沮丧的难度级别是该游戏的痛点。<ref>{{cite web| title = Mega Man ZX Metacritic Reviews| url = https://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ds/megamanzx?q=mega%20man%20zx| website = metacritic.com| access-date = 2008-04-10| archive-date = 2008-12-01| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20081201024848/http://www.metacritic.com/games/platforms/ds/megamanzx?q=mega%20man%20zx| dead-url = no}}</ref><br>
在游戏发行的当周，本作为日本第六最畅销电子游戏，总销量达到33,652份。<ref>{{cite web | author=Jenkins, David | date=July 14, 2006 | title=Mario Bros. Tops Japanese Charts For Sixth Week | url=https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/10080/Mario_Bros_Tops_Japanese_Charts_For_Sixth_Week.php | website=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | access-date=2010-06-13 | archive-date=2021-08-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210829070436/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/10080/Mario_Bros_Tops_Japanese_Charts_For_Sixth_Week.php | dead-url=no }}</ref>2006年年底该游戏在日本的总销量达到了94,341份。<ref>{{cite web | title=2006年テレビゲームソフト売り上げTOP500（ファミ通版） | url=http://geimin.net/da/db/2006_ne_fa/index.php | website=Geimin.net | language=ja | access-date=2010-06-13 | archive-date=2015-06-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626214525/http://geimin.net/da/db/2006_ne_fa/index.php | dead-url=yes }}</ref>此后本作的续作[[洛克人ZX·降临|洛克人ZX·降临]]宣布将在下一年发行。<ref>{{cite web | author=McWhertor, Michael | date=April 13, 2007 | title=Mega Man ZX Advent, Mega Man Star Force End Mega Man Drought | url=https://kotaku.com/252322/mega-man-zx-advent-mega-man-star-force-end-mega-man-drought | publisher=Kotaku | access-date=2010-06-13 | url-status=dead | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121014021948/http://kotaku.com/252322/mega-man-zx-advent-mega-man-star-force-end-mega-man-drought | archive-date=October 14, 2012}}</ref>

